             was indicted for for <rs id="t17980912-9-off48" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980912-9-off48" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980912-9-off48" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17980912-9-cd49" type="crimeDate">30th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-9-off48 t17980912-9-cd49"></join>, a wooden firkin, value 8d. and fifty-six pounds of butter, value 2l. 2s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17980912-9-victim114" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Bacon
                  <interp inst="t17980912-9-victim114" type="surname" value="Bacon"></interp>
